          <title>Top Five Central Banks</title>								                  <!--[0-1]-->
 	        <paragraph>The interest rate change is very important because it affects: unemployment rate, stock market, GDP, oil prices and money depreciation. The central banks involved this week consists in: Bank of Japan, Fed, Bank of England, Norges bank and the Swiss SNB.</paragraph>                        <!--[0-N]-->
