        <chapter>                                                               <!--[0-N]-->
          <title>Exchange rates</title>                                                      <!--[0-1]-->
          <paragraph>The exchange rate between two currencies is the rate at which one currency will be exchanged for another. It is also regarded as the value of one country’s currency in terms of another currency. The values are effects of interest rates changes.</paragraph>
